name.text: The Healthy Cleansing Webinar: How to supercharge your metabolism and vitality.
name.html: The Healthy Cleansing Webinar: How to supercharge your metabolism and vitality.

description.text:
Imagine feeling healthier than you have in years... 
Feeling more vital, more alive, and filled with positive energy... 
Imagine losing that extra stubborn weight, fitting into your favorite clothes.    Or just feeling "lighter" and less toxic. 
Wouldn't that make life a lot more enjoyable? 
Most people don't realize that the health of your skin and hair is proportional to the health of your intestinal system. A healthy intestinal system is the cornerstone of good health. 
So how do you do a proper cleanse? And what are the two most important steps that most people forget when it comes to cleansing successfully? 
That's exactly what I will explain in this webinar recording: Healthly Cleansing Methods: How to do a proper internal cleanse to supercharge your metabolism. 
In this webinar you will learn how to safely do 6 different kinds of cleanses: 

Scientific Juice Fasting (Hands-down the most powerful healing cleanse known to humanity)
The 10-Day Master Cleanse
The 1-Day Weekly Cleanse
The Gall-Bladder Flush 
The 60-Day Detox Cleanse
Smoothie Cleansing

 Online International Webinar: You can join and listen to this from anywhere in the world because it's online. 
The Live Webinar was recorded on April 24th, 2013.  Your Ticket will give you access to the RECORDING only!

description.text:
Take a scenic ride through the Ojai Valley.  Mix in new and old friends.  Throw in roadside snacks and a farm fresh feast after the finish.  Top it off with a little media hype and you are riding in the exciting energy of the Toad Fondo! 
  
When:     Saturday, April 26 , 2014 at 8 am 
  
Start:      The MOB Shop, 110 W Ojai Ave, Ojai, CA 93023  
  
Register here or at www.toadfondo.org 
  
Ride and raise funds for high school students to attend The Thacher School!
